echo "Welcome to FastBuilder Installer For Android!"
echo "Updating available APT packs..."
apt update -y && apt upgrade -y
echo "APT updated!"
echo "Install required APT packs..."
apt install nodejs -y
if [ $? -eq 0 ]; then
    echo "Successfully installed Nodejs!"
else
    echo -e "\033[31mUnable to install Nodejs!\033[0m"
fi
apt install unzip -y
if [ $? -eq 0 ]; then
    echo "Successfully installed Unzip!"
else
    echo "Unable to install Unzip, it might already installed in your device."
fi
echo "Creating directory..."
cd ~/
fbfolder="pro"
if [ ! -d "$fbfolder" ]; then
    mkdir "$fbfolder"
else
    echo "Removing & Updating FastBuilder..."
    rm -rf ~/pro
    mkdir "$fbfolder"
fi
echo "Created!"
file="/storage/emulated/0/tencent/QQfile_recv/Thor.zip"
if [ ! -f "$file" ]; then
    echo -e "\033[31mFailed to move files! You need to download FastBuilder's zip package, then retry again.\033[0m"
    exit
fi
echo "Moving archive..."
mv $file ~/pro
echo "Moved!"
cd ~/pro
unzip Thor.zip
if [ $? -eq 0 ]; then
    echo "Successfully Unzip!"
else
    echo -e "\033[31mFailed to Unzip! Please check your permission and retry again!\033[0m"
    exit
fi
cd ~/
echo "Creating script..."
rm -rf ~/fbpro
touch ~/fbpro
echo "File created!"
echo "Setting permission"
chmod +x ~/fbpro
echo "Set: 777"
echo "Writing file..."
echo "cd ~/pro && node SubF --max-old-space-size=2048" > ~/fbpro
echo "Installation finished, execute './fbpro' to run FastBuilder Pro Thor."
